                     <content styleCode="bold">
                        <br/> Tips for Managing Heartburn </content>
                     <br/> • Do not lie flat or bend over after eating. <br/> • Do not wear tight-fitting clothing around the stomach.<br/> • Do not eat before bedtime. <br/> • Raise the head of your bed. <br/> • Avoid heartburn-causing foods such as rich, spicy, fatty or fried foods, chocolate, caffeine,     alcohol and certain fruits and vegetables.      <br/> • Eat slowly and do not eat big meals.<br/> • If overweight, lose weight. <br/> • Quit smoking. <br/>
